### **05-FINDONE** =========================================
###
# BOOKS - Sucesso
# @name get_book_success
GET http://localhost:3002/books/{{livro.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json

###
# BOOKS - Falha (404)
GET http://localhost:3002/books/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json

###
